-- Lombard Odier Hires MacIntosh From Standard Life to Head Rates in Geneva
-- Anchalee Worrachate
-- 2010-06-17T10:02:39Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-06-17/lombard-odier-hires-macintosh-from-standard-life-to-head-rates-in-geneva.html

          
          
             Lombard Odier Investment Managers
said it hired Gregor MacIntosh as head of rates from Standard
Life Plc.  
 MacIntosh will be based in Geneva, Switzerland, and report
to head of fixed-income and currencies Stephane Monier, Lombard
said in an e-mailed statement today.  
